Package: caspr
Type: Package
Title: Cellular Automata for Spatial Pressure in R
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2015-06-12
Author: Florian Schneider, Alex Genin, Vishwesha Guttal, Sonia Kefi
Maintainer: Florian D. Schneider <florian.schneider@univ-montp2.fr>
URL: https://github.com/fdschneider/caspr
Description: The project package for a study on spatial indicators of 
    catastrophic shifts. Functions to run and analyse a set of cellular 
    automata models that implement a spatially explicit pressure. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Additional_repositories: https://github.com/fdschneider/
Imports: 
  foreach,
  animation,
  moments,
  spatialwarnings
Suggests: testthat,
          doSNOW
